To generate a signed apk , we should follow the steps given below-
1-> In the menu bar, click Build -> Generate Signed APK.
2-> Select the module you would like to release from the drop down, and click Next.
3-> Create you new keystore or if you have an existing one then click next after choosing you key store.
4-> If you are creating a new keystore , then fill out the necessary details and then click next.
5-> Change the build type to release and click on finish and it will automatically save the signed apk in our app folder\. 
